cu.explanation_en: Setting the integrity algorithm to the unknown enum 'nia9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting maxMIMO_layers to 0 will cause MIMO configuration failure and prevent proper signal processing.
du.explanation_zh: 將 maxMIMO_layers 設定為 0 會導致 MIMO 配置失敗，並阻止正確的信號處理。
